snippet.title: Backrooms Lost Dimension | Epic Games Store
snippet.description:
Backrooms: Between Lost Dimension is a single-player video game developed by SG Studios using Unreal Engine 5.4.

The official Epic Games Store page will be available on June 15, 2024, and the game will be released on October 31, 2024.
